            {
              "id": "CVE-2011-4116",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2011-4116"
              },
              "helpUri": "https://scout.docker.com/v/CVE-2011-4116?s=debian&n=perl&ns=debian&t=deb&osn=debian&osv=13&vr=%3C%3D5.40.1-6",
              "help": {
                "text": "_is_safe in the File::Temp module for Perl does not properly handle symlinks.\n\n---\n- perl <unfixed> (unimportant; bug https://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?bug=776268)\nhttp://thread.gmane.org/gmane.comp.security.oss.general/6174/focus=6177\nhttps://github.com/Perl-Toolchain-Gang/File-Temp/issues/14\n",
