            {
              "id": "CVE-2025-69645",
              "name": "OsPackageVulnerability",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2025-69645"
              },
              "helpUri": "https://scout.docker.com/v/CVE-2025-69645?s=debian&n=binutils&ns=debian&t=deb&osn=debian&osv=13&vr=%3C%3D2.44-3",
              "help": {
                "text": "Binutils objdump contains a denial-of-service vulnerability when processing a crafted binary with malformed DWARF debug information. A logic error in the handling of DWARF compilation units can result in an invalid offset_size value being used inside byte_get_little_endian, leading to an abort (SIGABRT). The issue was observed in binutils 2.44. A local attacker can trigger the crash by supplying a malicious input file.\n\n---\n- binutils <unfixed> (unimportant)\nhttps://sourceware.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=33637\nhttps://sourceware.org/git/gitweb.cgi?p=binutils-gdb.git;h=cdb728d4da6184631989b192f1022c219dea7677\nbinutils not covered by security support\n",
                "markdown": "> Binutils objdump contains a denial-of-service vulnerability when processing a crafted binary with malformed DWARF debug information. A logic error in the handling of DWARF compilation units can result in an invalid offset_size value being used inside byte_get_little_endian, leading to an abort (SIGABRT). The issue was observed in binutils 2.44. A local attacker can trigger the crash by supplying a malicious input file.\n\n---\n- binutils <unfixed> (unimportant)\nhttps://sourceware.org/bugzilla/show_bug.cgi?id=33637\nhttps://sourceware.org/git/gitweb.cgi?p=binutils-gdb.git;h=cdb728d4da6184631989b192f1022c219dea7677\nbinutils not covered by security support\n\n|                                                                                              |\n|Package         pkg:deb/debian/binutils@2.44-3?os_distro=trixie&os_name=debian&os_version=13  |\n|Affected range  <=2.44-3                                                                      |\n|Fixed version   not fixed                                                                     |\n"
              },
              "properties": {
                "affected_version": "<=2.44-3",
                "cvssV3_severity": "LOW",
                "fixed_version": "not fixed",
                "purls": [
                  "pkg:deb/debian/binutils@2.44-3?os_distro=trixie&os_name=debian&os_version=13"
                ],
                "security-severity": "3.1",
                "tags": [
